text:
C5 is an American musical artist and rapper who has released 6 music albums. C5 is also the founder of the popular apparel Dorm Flow®.
The young creative is a dynamic, conscious, and innovative rapper,songwriter from Oakland, CA. He prides himself on making music that is an honest representation of his life experiences. His music tells the story of what it’s like to be from the streets, remain true to yourself, and fight for a life better than the one he’s seen. You can hear the duality of his street and college education in his pen game.
Early life.
C5 was born in 10 March, 1994 in Oakland, California, United States. His birth name is Christopher Fives but he is best known as stage name C5.
Career.
C5 solidified his music career in 2013 and released his first mixtape/album titled "Dorm Flow".
